  "Using the 1.5 x IQR rule, a data set has Q1 = 10 and Q3 = 20. Which value would be an outlier?": "",
  "36": "",
  "25": "",
  "30": "",
  "5": "",
  "IQR = 20 - 10 = 10. Upper fence = 20 + 1.5(10) = 35. Lower fence = 10 - 1.5(10) = -5. Since 36 > 35, it is an outlier.": "",
