  "What does 'lower fence' mean in the context of outliers?": "",
  "The first quartile": "",
  "The minimum value in the data set": "",
  "The value Q1 - 1.5 x IQR, below which data points are considered outliers": "",
  "The mean minus the standard deviation": "",
  "The lower fence is Q1 - 1.5 x IQR. Any data value below this fence is classified as a potential lower outlier.": "",
